    {
      "id": "a81cd75b-178a-49bf-a26c-b14dafc599c4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Deep Learning has grown in popularity in educational research and prediction of student performance is no exception. Review uses 46 papers using Deep Learning for the prediction of student performance. ",
