    {
      "id": "cbbfd290-2ceb-48e3-b499-c06d52cc3ff1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Most common models are DNN and CNN-LSTM and, for the most part, these models have been shown to outperform other alternative methods in predictive performance (specifically accuracy). Along the datasets used, OULAD is the most popular one. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
